message.content:
Analysis of the Target Image
--------------------------------
There are actually two separate little “buildings” shown:

•  Left‐Hand Structure (5 blocks total):
   –  Bottom layer: one long yellow rectangular block lying flat, plus two tall green rectangular “pillars” standing vertically on that yellow block.  
   –  Above the pillars: another horizontal yellow rectangular block bridging them, with an orange triangular “roof” piece perched on top.  

•  Right‐Hand Structure (3 blocks total):
   –  Bottom layer: two orange cylinders standing upright.  
   –  Top layer: one green rectangular block lying horizontally across (bridging) the two cylinders.  

Hence there are 8 total blocks used in two layers (the roof piece on the left structure makes a small third layer above the yellow “bridge”).

Matching Blocks From the Dictionary
-------------------------------------
Below is which dictionary index corresponds to each piece (no rotations allowed other than how they appear in the dictionary):

•  Left Building:
   1.  Bottom yellow horizontal plank → Dictionary index 5  
   2.  Two green vertical pillars → Dictionary index 3 (used twice)  
   3.  Top yellow horizontal plank → Dictionary index 5 (used again)  
   4.  Orange triangular roof → Dictionary index 13  

•  Right Building:
   1.  Two orange cylinders (upright) → Dictionary index 9 (used twice)  
   2.  Green horizontal block bridging the cylinders → Dictionary index 1  

Complete List of Indices Used
--------------------------------
[1, 3, 3, 5, 5, 9, 9, 13]

Proposed Assembly Order
------------------------
{
  Step1: Move block with index 5            // bottom yellow plank (left structure)
  Step2: Move block with index 3            // first green vertical pillar
  Step3: Move block with index 3            // second green vertical pillar
  Step4: Move block with index 5            // top yellow plank over pillars
  Step5: Move block with index 13           // orange triangular roof
  Step6: Move block with index 9            // first orange cylinder (right structure)
  Step7: Move block with index 9            // second orange cylinder
  Step8: Move block with index 1            // green rectangular block bridging cylinders
}
